---
metadata: {
    partial_name: 'Ecommerce | Reviews | Review List'
}
---
{% comment %}
    Swappable reviews list (the AJAX swap target's contents — items only).
    Rendered initially by review_section.liquid and by api/reviews/list-results.
    The pager is a separate, persistent ins-table (see review_section.liquid).

    Params:
    - reviews : get_reviews items ({ results })
{% endcomment %}
<div class="review-list">
    {%- for review in reviews.results -%}
        <div class="review-item">
            <div class="review-item__header">
                <div class="review-item__user">
                    <span class="review-item__name">{{ review.reviewer_first_name }} {{ review.reviewer_last_name }}</span>
                    {% include 'modules/ecommerce/reviews/star_rating', rating: review.rating, size: 14 %}
                </div>
                <span class="review-item__date">{{ review.created_at | date: '%b %d, %Y' }}</span>
            </div>
            <p class="review-item__body">{{ review.review_content }}</p>
        </div>
    {%- endfor -%}
</div>
